content: Hello! Thank you for contacting XYZ Home Services. May I have your name, please?
I just need my AC looked at. Why do you need my name?
We ask for your name to make sure your appointment is scheduled correctly and to keep you updated about your service. Could you please provide your name?
I'd prefer not to share that now. Can we just move on?
That's okay. We can continue! Can you please provide the address where you need HVAC service?
